{
  "stem": "766.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It needed-- I could use this medication, to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he wanted to pay me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, I don't want any more, any money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I said, who needs, now, anything?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- we don't need anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To me, it was the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until it started getting, somehow, because we have to move to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a teacher and a principal of a school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Majerkiewitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that wasn't the time of-- that-- that-- for such things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I am not going for the-- the-- the routine, what's going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was we went to a rabbi and was a little reception.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, the style was like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And anyhow, I didn't have the money for this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was, already, the atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There wasn't a wedding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- the atmosphere [? wasn't ?] [? clear. ?] And anyhow, if it-- it would be, I didn't care for-- for these things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we-- we rented, sublet, two rooms in someplace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- and we got organized a little bit for the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we didn't know then will break out, the war, and everything will be over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever I have, the little money, because my father didn't work so long.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So and was dead so many years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- so this what I had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So later it was destroyed in one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they throw me out from this apartment again, when-- when the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he had a family, sisters and brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but-- to-- it happened to be the same street we moved in, but by accident.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One brother survived because he lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I met him later.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
